flowchart LR
    subgraph Operator["Operator (agentctl / deploy.sh)"]
        CLI[gcloud commands]
    end

    subgraph GCP["Google Cloud Platform"]
        CB[Cloud Build]
        AR[(Artifact Registry<br/>remote-agent image)]
        SM[(Secret Manager<br/>id-token<br/>anthropic-api-key)]
        IAM[IAM<br/>runtime SA + secretAccessor]
        CR[Cloud Run service<br/>agent-id<br/>max-instances=1]
    end

    Dev[Claude Code<br/>on laptop]
    API[Anthropic API]

    CLI -->|builds image| CB
    CB -->|pushes| AR
    CLI -->|mints token| SM
    CLI -->|binds policy| IAM
    CLI -->|gcloud run deploy| CR

    AR -.image.-> CR
    SM -.mounted as env.-> CR
    IAM -.authorizes mount.-> CR

    Dev -->|HTTPS + Bearer token<br/>POST /mcp run_task| CR
    CR -->|claude -p / Agent SDK| API
